<p class="ql-align-center">△//李清照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200815/70f166c50c56405ca7b2f3376ee1c8a5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//辛弃疾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200815/5b1cb74236444c89b0beb2ec87d168cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>△//</strong>张养浩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是一处以泉水众多、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风光明秀而着称于世的美丽城市。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南城内百泉争涌，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分布着久负盛名的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趵突泉 、黑虎泉、五龙潭、珍珠泉四大泉群，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来到济南，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可以充分领略</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泉水文化的魅力。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200815/7b5208e8c85048a78a5d0cb11fa0e882.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
