<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200815/83449a252ddf4f17a2cc6a4981b0b982.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//五龙潭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200815/73eace3875ea4f3dbc55493d57c05802.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//珍珠泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200815/87697ed600f24554a328df28699020d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//涌泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200815/11eb0ae52ffc46498cece0293b9a7129.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//书院泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200815/16940991a28e413d86f2b2120df5f404.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//百脉泉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南是我国北方重要的曲艺之乡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长久以来就以“曲山艺海”美名享誉神州大地。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与北京、天津并称为曲艺界的三大码头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200815/fbbbfdbcfff44b3e9305aa387481c7f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南皮影、济南面塑、济南剪纸、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">龙山黑陶制作技艺、东阿阿胶制作技艺……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南有丰富的非遗资源，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蕴藏着丰富的文化遗韵和民俗渊源，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有很多“国宝级”的非遗大师。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200815/ddd0f1f8fa77410e8fbd4115591367b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//龙山黑陶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200815/d09884d4d7464efbb4485cc4e05b3896.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//阿胶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200815/577e15de97b54e6e8c58d503c5424ced.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//南留张银器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200815/8f4f824bf76a4695863925f56a629038.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//济南兔子王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200815/43a0030369dc4a648d8c8fecf28e7aa6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//商河鼓子秧歌</p>
<h1>美食诱惑</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南是“美食之都”，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲁菜原料鲜活，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">注重本味，刀工精细，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火工讲究，富于变化，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生活在济南的童鞋有口福啦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200815/006a1fbedd2f4bf4be732cc821d312ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//盘丝饼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200815/be031f5c915b41c8a026003e8eb90a80.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//糖醋鲤鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200815/c04a810e8b284d099740b4fbdbcfe060.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//爆三样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200815/04d1c138aba3486bb2750f54a7e1a000.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//雪野鱼头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200815/775b371e33b744e38b25a244e9cf3ea1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//九转大肠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200815/ac242f96fc5046ebbe647f2ecc519254.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//爆炒腰花</p>
<p><strong>活力诱惑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南也是一座运动之城，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大大小小的公园</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">散布在城市各个角落。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200815/2a8d14d2ec7f41e99cd8f52428df2f06.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
