<h1>产业诱惑</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南正着力推进</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打造国家中心城市，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十大千亿级产业加速崛起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">软件、机器人产业、人工智能、医养健康等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">产业如火如荼地发展。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未来的你，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">定能在济南一展抱负、大有作为。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200815/0f79a4cf864b443694793c7c3d1fbb19.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//高新片区</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200815/b1d27aac632a40dbb3ab9e3cbc19e823.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//齐鲁软件园</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200815/ee0f345ce63a4f0fb36c609a1653a0ab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">△//汉峪金谷</p>
<h1>美景诱惑</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然，济南的美景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是一张靓丽名片，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为旅游名城，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">济南值得你的青睐。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200815/b2dbd6d970c64c909d0e25124eaba784.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
